data.description: This beautifully updated craftsman style home with an assumable loan at 2.75% awaits you. Featuring: 4 bedrooms | 4 bathrooms | home office | main floor laundry |walk-out fully finished basement w/wet bar | large outdoor space | paver patio |rear deck | custom kitchen w/granite countertops and stainless appliances | gas fireplace | re-finished maple flooring | open porch | 3 car garage| and a very spacious primary bedroom suite w/walk-in closet . This property will have you captivated from the moment you drive up. If you are looking for a quality built, well cared for home, in a fantastic location look no further!
